data.description: Welcome home to 114 Poplar Grove Crescent located in the beautiful Burnetts Mill neighborhood of Suffolk! This 3 bed 2 bath ranch sits on a quiet cul-de-sac just down the street from the community playground and clubhouse. Large bedrooms including a primary suite with an attached full bath and large walk-in closet. The spacious layout welcomes you to a large living room with cathedral ceilings, a natural gas fireplace, and a bar area leading to the kitchen. Off of the living room is a deck leading to the large fenced backyard that has seasonal canoe/kayak access to the Rountree South Pond which extends all the way from Burnetts Mill to Hillpoint. Minutes from Obici Hospital, RT 10, 58, 258, 460, and Interstates 664, 64, 264, and more! Easy commute to Smithfield Packing, Navy Exchange, Shipyards, Military Installations, and most major Hampton Roads attractions! Book your private showing today!
